Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fair, Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only taking meat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault meat sticks to the side dish. {??? lit is just "sticks/goes along" so no clue, maybe sticks to her chopsticks, or something completely different altogether; probably "meat sticks [to the less delicious dish that's in that pot]" tho I have no clue what they're eating and what's supposed to go with meat there and I don't care enough to check}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's you who's only taking meat, Yuu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath that green onion, \Nit's nothing but meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How strange! Maybe it got stuck to the green onion?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there'll be plenty of meat again. {lit: gotta make it full of meat}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Panpuru pinpuru pamupoppun! {Mami's transformation spell}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your attention. {more specifically "I'm sorry if the entertainment wasn't up to your standards"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So great!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.26,0:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perukko raburin kurukuru rinkuru!{Persia's transformation spell}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.26,0:03:44.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Pararin ririkaru parapora majikaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Blue scroll, red scroll, yellow scroll!" {"Aomakigami\Nakamakigami kiimakigami"\N(tongue twister) }
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai's sure late.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.73,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's going to boil down soon! {probably means that the water in the pot is about to run out}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, let's start without her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.48,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Made it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with "Bamboo bush got burned." {"Takeyabu yaketa"\N - (Palindrome )}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a tongue twister.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.20,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about,\N "The other guest eats persimmons"? {"Tonari no kyaku ha yoku kakikuu kyaku da."}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Better pick an easier one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Toukyou tokkyo kyokakyoku"}"Toukyou patent office."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.87,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{"kaeru pyokopyoko mi pyokopyoko..."}"Frogs hopping, three hops..."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{"...awasete pyokopyoko mu pyokopyoko"}"...gather hopping, six hops."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.81,0:05:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the first turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.90,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.03,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us together are \Nthe shining magical squad Sun Vulcan! {??? idk, that san can be "three ..." but idc enough to dig}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.66,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the stuff playing\Nnow is my video.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.33,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I collected Love Powers by transforming\N into the beauty Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's impressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's also Persia's\Nwonderful boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have one too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one too, Yuu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. A suggestion.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we three gathered \Nand went to a hot spring together,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,let's call our boyfriends one by one
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and introduce them to the other two.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, first is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda shy about it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Persia, what's your boyfriend's name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaku and Riki.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.49,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But Riki's actually\NSayo-san's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Riki?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you calling for?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.46,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd introduce Gaku\Nand Riki to Yuu and Mai.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Gaku?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.79,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, just you will do for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm just a spare for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.93,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put Yuu on now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Morisawa Yuu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! I've heard about you\Nfrom Persia sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good things?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.64,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I heard you're\Na really unique girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Next, I'll put Mai on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kazuki Mai.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai is putting on some airs.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Mai-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki-san, you have a cool voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're... making me blush!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when have you been\N such a sissy, Riki? {/effeminate}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? When Persia come back on the line?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.36,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, next time bring\NYuu-chan and Mai-chan home.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.73,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute girls are your ultimate weakness, so it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuu and Mai are both very cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Even if it's true, don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how is your joint trip going?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With just three, you're one\Nshort for playing mahjong.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, you big dummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, while watching \Nmy videos from back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're gossiping about our memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess a lot has happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very happy with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.24,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love you both, Gaku and Riki.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When Gaku returns, I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.09,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't let Sayo-san bully you too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You stabbed my weak spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.49,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Persia. Don't overheat from\Nsoaking too long in the hot spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business.{resume}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please expect souvenirs.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Riki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Persia's boyfriend is absolutely cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely gonna be a fan of his.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm still a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's continue watching Persia's video.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki Mai, going in!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mai.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us together are The Candies!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's playing now is Mai's video.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.18,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In it, Mai transforms into Magical Emi and becomes a magician. {supposedly it's mai speaking? don't care}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, next is Mai's turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Call him, right away! {her boyfriend}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, Kazuki Mai, calling.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.11,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai, what's your boyfriend's name?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! He's not my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just Shou.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So Shou's his name?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mai?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You're calling me so suddenly.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgot something?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.89,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, I thought I'd introduce you \Nto Yuu and Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's an honor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll put Persia on.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayami Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're dabbling in boxing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always making me worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the one causing worry to the other?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.81,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's the girl who whines\Nevery time she slips up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mean! Shou, you jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai, why did you kick me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicking Shou's leg is my habit.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad I'm on the other end of this phone!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.64,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, I'm Morisawa Yuu.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I've heard about you\Nfrom Mai sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Good things?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.17,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. Well, anyway, I heard you're a really cheerful girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I'll put Mai on, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou, do you miss me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what are you doing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With just three, you're one\Nshort for playing mahjong.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.16,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. There's no way innocent girls \Nlike us would play such naughty games. {an unexpected piece of sound wisdom from this anime}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.98,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're watching my video from back then and talking about our memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be fond remembrances,\Nyour time with Magic Carat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.25,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, just now I showed\Nmy magic to Yuu and Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it turn out well?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yup, it was perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I only fumbled it a bit!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai's really good at magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. She'll surely be\Na wonderful magician.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep doing my best!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overheat from soaking too long in the hot spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.90,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you try not to get yourself hurt during boxing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.08,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou-san, good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai's boyfriend is cool too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai, you seem down somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.93,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered about Topo\Nwhile talking to Shou about magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.79,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Topo left without\Neven saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.03,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also now remembering Geragera,\NMesomeso, and Puripuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.46,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Posi\Nand Nega are doing. {don't expect me to check if any of those are actully in her show}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're all doing great.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we're so serious and pensive now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't suit us at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.94,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. \NLet's have some shots and enjoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, you brought sake?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're such a delinquent!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not be so prudish this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, sit down.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, to our memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To the unbounded future ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm last!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.34,0:20:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Topo, you're the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.94,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Geragera, Mesomeso,\Nand Puripuri, you're all great. {I trust those are all a thing in her show (don't even know which one this is), but these are also onomas for "roaring (with laughter) / sobbing / angrily"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.11,0:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Posi and Nega, you still alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.60,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaku and Riki, you big dummies!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou, you jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you're really into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshio, what a hunk. {ii otoko}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, you traitor!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.94,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for taking advantage of the fuss!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Are you going to hit me for real?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.06,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, give me another glass.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai, you have such bad habits.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, she's bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.82,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's playing\Nnow is my video.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.22,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Morisawa Yuu, can transform\Ninto Creamy Mami using magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.37,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.00,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and call your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.57,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the phone number is...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, your hand is shaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.10,0:22:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep chattering in my ear, \NI'll dial the wrong number.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Ootomo.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshio?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.19,0:22:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Yuu? Why are you calling like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You forgot something?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.91,0:22:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't make fun of your Yuu-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.68,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you drunk?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so strict.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.54,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to my friends now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.22,0:22:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.09,0:22:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know, Yuu never gets tired of bragging about you, Toshio-san. {boastful talk about one's love life; speaking fondly about one's sweetheart; going on about one's love affairs}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.49,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You jealous?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.85,0:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be Toshio's bride.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we decide that?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.02,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just did!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.24,0:23:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have a wedding\Nat the white chapel on the hill.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.74,0:23:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a wedding dress.\NToshio's in a white morning suit. {says "white morning" for some reason but i think she's just mixing up those english words bc she's drunk}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.16,0:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Enveloped in the organ's\Nsound and celebrating people,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.92,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we two walk down along the virgin road\N as I hold a pure white bouquet in my hand. {probably means the church isle}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.73,0:23:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you have such\N a well-developed imagination!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.97,0:23:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give me more sake!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll invite you to my wedding too, Mai.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {??? maybe it's the same girl, then "I promise!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.13,0:23:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.31,0:23:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshio-san, I'm Persia.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.06,0:23:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.93,0:23:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.53,0:23:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Shou-san's, \Nyour voice is cool too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.62,0:23:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.08,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, people say it a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.79,0:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toshio!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.50,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when are you such a sissy? {same as before}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.00,0:24:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.89,0:24:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yuu?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.26,0:24:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, both Mai-chan and Persia-chan sound pretty cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.84,0:24:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're praising them already.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.56,0:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshio, you jerk! {?? idk what she says originally so this can stay}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.04,0:24:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshio, you... Nibushima You!\N{(Mizushima --> Nibushima )}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.35,0:24:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not making any sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.02,0:24:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how is your hot springs trip going?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.90,0:24:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.98,0:24:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually I have my hands full\Nall the time, looking after you.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:34.91,0:24:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to take a break sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.99,0:24:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:38.87,0:24:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what're you doing there?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.79,0:24:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With just three, you're one\Nshort for playing mahjong.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.25,0:24:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, earlier, we saw Mai's magic,\Nthen we were watching our old videos
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.55,0:24:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and discussing our memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:53.51,0:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, my video\Nfrom back then is playing.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.59,0:24:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.88,0:25:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they say, "Get three women together, something something mayhem." {citing 女三人寄れば姦しい = "three women together are noisy" - 女 is character for woman and 姦しい (noisy) looks like three woman characters; here he replaces the noisy part with "whatever it was" - either he doesn't remember it or tries not to offend anyone}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.02,0:25:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.19,0:25:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get three women together... beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.90,0:25:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get three women together... sexy!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.94,0:25:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you three really are cocky!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.70,0:25:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thanks for the compliment. {??? can only assume they misheard namaiki (cocky) for nagaiki (long life)}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.62,0:25:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.99,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.20,0:25:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overheat from soaking\Ntoo long in the hot spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.66,0:25:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.54,0:25:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.21,0:25:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.00,0:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Toshio...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.88,0:25:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.44,0:25:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:30.59,0:25:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mai, you have bad habits.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.76,0:25:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.37,0:25:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.34,0:25:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you three, \Nyou'd better not drink anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.29,0:25:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.32,0:25:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Another glass!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:46.94,0:25:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't drink anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.73,0:25:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... gimme another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.53,0:25:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good.
